  "title": "[수족구병/남성역이수한의원]수족구병 원인과증상",
  "addDate": "2013. 6. 5.",
  "categoryNo": "32",
  "parentCategoryNo": "32",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110169514085",
  "html_size": 187855,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110169514085\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110169514085\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">[수족구병/남성역이수한의원]</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 0, 124);\">수족구병 원인과증상</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">여름철이 되면 각종 질병의 발생위험은 크게 증가하게 됩니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">특히 면역력이 약한 영유아들은 이러한 질병에 걸리기</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;쉬울 뿐아니라&nbsp;결렸을 때 심각한 문제가 될 수 있습니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">그리고 수족구병은 지금과 같은 시기 잘 나타나는 대표적인 질환입니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130605_218/isuhani_1370413611989nQQJX_PNG/%BC%F6%C1%B7%B1%B81.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"336\" height=\"190\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 336px; rheight: 190px;\" id=\"20130605_218/isuhani_1370413611989nQQJX_PNG/%BC%F6%C1%B7%B1%B81.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A69D6065')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130605_218/isuhani_1370413611989nQQJX_PNG/%BC%F6%C1%B7%B1%B81.PNG?type=w3\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">최근 뉴스에서 개인위생을 철저히 관리를 당부했을 정도로 수족구병은 뜨거운 관심사입니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">수족구병이란 입 그리고 손이나 발에 발진이 나타나는 전염성 질병으로 아이가 평소와 달리 </p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">해당부위에 무엇인가 생겨났다면 수족구병 초기증상을 의심해 볼 필요가 있습니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130605_285/isuhani_1370413890923C50mJ_PNG/%BC%F6%C1%B7%B1%B83.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"408\" height=\"300\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 408px; rheight: 300px;\" id=\"20130605_285/isuhani_1370413890923C50mJ_PNG/%BC%F6%C1%B7%B1%B83.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A69D6065')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130605_285/isuhani_1370413890923C50mJ_PNG/%BC%F6%C1%B7%B1%B83.PNG?type=w3\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">수족구병 원인은 바이러스감염 때문이며 여러 바이러스 중 콕사키바이러스와 </p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">엔테로바이러스가 몸에 침투하여 수족구병을 발생시킵니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">콕사키바이러스는 주로 발열과 두통 증상이 나타나는데 </p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">감기와 비슷하게 몸에 열이나면서 두통을 호소하게 됩니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">또한 갑자기 구토나 무기력증과 같은 증상이 나타날 수 있습니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;물론 이러한 일반적 증상들으로 수족구병이라 단정짓기는 어렵지만 </p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">시간이 지나도 증상이 계속되면 반드시 내원하여 검사를 받는 것이 좋습니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130605_256/isuhani_1370414722122XRcAy_PNG/%BC%F6%C1%B7%B1%B84.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"377\" height=\"278\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 377px; rheight: 278px;\" id=\"20130605_256/isuhani_1370414722122XRcAy_PNG/%BC%F6%C1%B7%B1%B84.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A69D6065')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130605_256/isuhani_1370414722122XRcAy_PNG/%BC%F6%C1%B7%B1%B84.PNG?type=w3\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">문제는 입이나 손, 발 주변에 수포나 분홍색 구진등이 생기는 경우입니다 </p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">엔테로바이러스에 의해서 나타나는 수족구병은 뇌염, 무균성 뇌수막염 등</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;신경계 합병증을 동반하게 되는데 이는 생명과도 연결되는 매우 위험한 질환입니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">따라서 수족구병 초기증상이 나타났을때 수족구병 원인 바이러스가 무엇인지</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;검사를 통해 확인하고 아이가 잘 회복될 수 있게 부모는 각별한 관심을 가질 필요가 있습니다. </p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">그렇지 않고 쉽게생각했다가는 돌이킬 수 없는 상황이 초래될 수 있습니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130605_280/isuhani_1370415432757EGVky_PNG/%BC%F6%C1%B7%B1%B85.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"298\" height=\"279\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 298px; rheight: 279px;\" id=\"20130605_280/isuhani_1370415432757EGVky_PNG/%BC%F6%C1%B7%B1%B85.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A69D6065')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130605_280/isuhani_1370415432757EGVky_PNG/%BC%F6%C1%B7%B1%B85.PNG?type=w3\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 0, 124);\">수족구병 예방을 위한 방법</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- 손발을 깨끗이 씻고 청결을 유지한다</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 전염성 질환을 예방하는 첫번째는 몸의 청결을 유지하는 것입니다 우리 생활 곳곳은 오염 물질이&nbsp; </p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 존재하고 이는 아이의 면역력을 손쇱게 떨어트리는 원인으로 작용합니다 </p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 따라서 외출 후 손발을 깨끗히 씻고 몸을 향상 청결하도록 관리해야 합니다</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;- 사람이 많이 모이는 장소를 피한다</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;전염성 질환은 사람이 많이 모이는 곳에서 유발될 확률이 높습니다. 외출을 일부러 피하지 않더라도 </p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 사람이 많이 모이는 장소에 아이를 데려가는 것은 주의해야 합니다.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 면역력 강화를 위한 도움을 받는다</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 아이가 평소 잦은 질병에 걸리거나 몸이 허약하다면 면역력과 몸의 기능을 강화시키는 과정이 필요합니다</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;영양보충이나 휴식도 방법이겠지만 한방치료와 같은 치료적 도움을 받는 것도 방법입니다</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p> </div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
